urlText: L2 Randwick and L3 Kingsford Line weekend trackwork
content:
From 5am Saturday 26 September to 1am Monday 28 September, buses will replace light rail between Central Chalmers Street and Randwick or Juniors Kingsford on the L2 Randwick Line and the L3 Kingsford Line, due to planned maintenance works. Replacement buses will run daily in both directions as follows:
  • Every 10-15 minutes, from 5am to 7am.
  • Every 6-10 minutes, from 7am to 7pm.
  • Every 10-15 minutes, from 7pm to 1am.
Light rail services between Circular Quay and Central Chalmers Street will run at a temporary changed frequency of every 8 minutes in both directions throughout the whole weekend. Alternative transport such as trains or regular bus services may be available, use the Trip Planner to check your options. Please allow extra travel time and use the nearby replacement bus stop locations.
subtitle: L2 Randwick and L3 Kingsford Line weekend trackwork
